org.apache.juneau.internal

Class UnmodifiableArray<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.internal.UnmodifiableArray<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Array element type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>

    public class UnmodifiableArray<T>
extends Object
implements List<T>
    Simple read-only wrapper around an object array.

    Allows for forward or reverse access to elements of an array without being able to modify the array and without involving copying the array.
